Nick Wilton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nick_Wilton 0 Nicholas Wilton (born 8 March 1957) is an English actor and scriptwriter. Best known for playing Mr Lister in the BBC soap opera EastEnders as a recurring character, Wilton has also appeared in Carrott's Lib, Fast Forward and Jackanory.
